sp.
</taxonomicName>
and sixty ciliate specimens were found attached with 
<specimenCount id="9D4D70E6FFFEFFB4FDC13115FD56FE75" box="[605,726,367,393]" pageId="4" pageNumber="496" type="male">nine males</specimenCount>
of the same species from 
<quantity id="4CB3168AFFFEFFB4FC663115FBC1FE76" box="[1018,1089,367,394]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.02" pageId="4" pageNumber="496" unit="m" value="202.0">202 m</quantity>
